PEOPLE
v.
CONTRERAS S215516 Supreme Court of California September 14, 2016 Votes: Canil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division Three, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of People v. Conley (2016) 63 Cal.4th 646 , 203 Cal.Rptr.3d 622 , 373 P.3d 435 . (See Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)

Corrigan, J., was absent and did not participate.
